{"tid":1982171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"出道六年Red Velvet小分隊形成 神仙顏值Irene澀琪即將出道！","createTime":"2020-04-21T05:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T00:36:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2219ea911c1eeef3992c95158d167b348f8cd8","tid":1982171,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet出道至今已經產生許多膾炙人口的歌曲，每每回歸都會造成轟動，最近有消息指出，Red Velvet的Irene與澀琪將要組成小分隊，這也是他們出道六年來的第一個小分隊，讓所有粉絲都非常期待他們兩人的組合。<br />\n<br />\n究竟他們會組成什麼樣的組合，又會走什麼樣的風格呢？至今還沒有確切答案，但是消息指出Irene與澀琪現在已經傾心在專輯的製作，不知道什麼時候會正式出道，在那之前，粉絲們就好好期待吧，相信Irene與澀琪會帶給我們更多驚喜的！"},{"pid":"cdd011c426aecdf7b6dbccbc13101727b8983c1b","tid":1982171,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.pop.tw.weibo.sina.com.tw/images/user_upload/04/84/6f/04846fae4470b84c16871723d6c16d3a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.pop.tw.weibo.sina.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fuser_upload%2F04%2F84%2F6f%2F04846fae4470b84c16871723d6c16d3a.jpeg&h=8c55b4af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.pop.tw.weibo.sina.com.tw/images/user_upload/d1/da/f6/d1daf6534d458dcde461bfe737558efa.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.pop.tw.weibo.sina.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fuser_upload%2Fd1%2Fda%2Ff6%2Fd1daf6534d458dcde461bfe737558efa.jpeg&h=f1fb0f88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20d0053c601fbbdd63f8fb6828b9332f06c047ba","tid":1982171,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59a9b9d5b49609da7b954e99c9e92ad82688264","tid":1982171,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"Irene Wendy Joy Yeri 就夠了"},{"pid":"f6332d2c2182d82368b38fe7e42c53f6b959d93e","tid":1982171,"uid":96941,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0